data.description: Better than new! Beautiful home located in one of the best neighborhoods In Cedar City. Kitchen features new high end Kitchen Aid appliances, dual fuel stove with two electric ovens and gas burners, french door refrigerator, 3 shelf dishwasher, new granite counter tops, beautiful red and white oak hardwood floors newly refinished, new sink, faucet and garbage disposal. All appliances have 3 year transferable warranty through Boulevard Home Furnishings. Home has fresh paint and new carpets. All bathrooms have new toilets, sinks and faucets, 1/2 bath on main level has a new vanity. New tile floor in family/sunroom. Plantation shutters throughout main level. TV in living room with sound bar and subwoofer will be included. Basement family room has new lighting and 2 new windows. More... Craft/dark room in basement has a sink and is plumbed for toilet. Seller will leave new toilet. New water softener. Seller requests to rent back 30 days to facilitate moving. Don't miss out on this beautiful home! Mesa Hills HOA annual dues cover maintaining several parks and open nature areas.
